It used below:
```
export interface Position {
    x: number;
    y: number;
}

export interface DropAnimation {
    duration: number;
    curve: string;
    moveTo: Position;
    opacity?: number;
    scale?: number;
}
```
There was used wrong type Position (from default  dom types), there is example of usage:
https://github.com/atlassian/react-beautiful-dnd/blob/master/docs/guides/drop-animation.md

Without these changes position using next fields: 
```
interface Position {
    readonly coords: Coordinates;
    readonly timestamp: number;
}
```

